name: Gemini 2.5 Pro Preview
description: Google's cutting-edge model with enhanced thinking and reasoning, multimodal understanding, advanced coding capabilities, and more.
comments: Google's most advanced model with superior reasoning and multimodal capabilities.

name: Gemini 2.0 Flash
description: Next generation features optimized for speed, thinking, realtime streaming, and multimodal generation with experimental image output capabilities.
comments: Fast and versatile model with text, image, and upcoming audio generation capabilities.

name: Gemini 2.0 Flash-Lite
description: Cost-efficient version of Gemini 2.0 Flash optimized for low latency applications while maintaining multimodal capabilities.
comments: Budget-friendly model with low latency for high-volume applications.

name: Gemini 1.5 Pro
description: Optimized for complex reasoning tasks requiring more intelligence. Supports audio, images, videos, and text inputs.
comments: Google's primary model with massive context window and multimodal capabilities.

name: Gemini 1.5 Flash
description: Fast and versatile performance across a diverse variety of tasks. Supports audio, images, videos, and text inputs.
comments: Fast and affordable model with large context window.

name: Gemini 1.5 Flash-8B
description: Compact 8B parameter model designed for high volume and lower intelligence tasks. Supports audio, images, videos, and text inputs.

name: Gemini 2.0 Flash Live
description: Specialized for low-latency bidirectional voice and video interactions. Supports audio, video, and text inputs with text and audio outputs.

name: Gemini Embedding
description: Advanced embedding model designed for measuring the relatedness of text strings. Creates high-quality vector representations.
comments: Powerful text embedding model for semantic search and analysis.

name: Imagen 3
description: Google's most advanced image generation model, converting text prompts into high-quality images.
comments: State-of-the-art image generation with superior quality and accuracy.

name: Veo 2
description: Advanced video generation model that transforms text and image inputs into high-quality videos.
comments: Cutting-edge video generation with impressive quality and fidelity.

name: Text Embedding Gecko
description: Google's text embedding model optimized for transforming text into vector representations. Suitable for search, classification, and clustering applications.
comments: Legacy embedding model, consider using Gemini Embedding for better performance.

name: Text Embedding 004
description: Google's advanced embedding model offering improved performance over Gecko. Creates high-quality vector representations for enhanced semantic understanding.
comments: Enhanced embedding model with larger context window.
